episodes.title: Deep Dive Into a Philippines Cult: Disturbing Media Followup
episodes.description:
I take a closer look at a topic I covered a few weeks ago: a video showing members of the Filipino CAFGU unit clashing with members of a militant Christian cult. What was supposed to be a tense but peaceful surrender took the worst possible turn.

Coverage of the incident can't seem to agree if the cult's leader was one of the fallen, or if another mysterious man quoted in only two articles was the real leader.

In this part 2 to my "The Filipino Cult Incident Video: Disturbing and Obscure Media" video, I examine the sources again, compare the evidence, and offer my opinions.
